{"title":"Python学习","uid":"909955b35c609fc9802a250199c95c9b","slug":"Python学习","date":"2023-01-21T08:40:00.000Z","updated":"2023-01-21T13:57:32.107Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Python学习.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://image-6zl.pages.dev/img/247402b1880511ebb6edd017c2d2eca2.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"2023年1月21日\"><a href=\"#2023年1月21日\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2023年1月21日\"></a>2023年1月21日</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"字符类\"><a href=\"#字符类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符类\"></a>字符类</h2><ul>\n<li><p><code>&quot;xxx&quot;</code>和<code>&#39;xxx&#39;</code>_字符串</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>&#39;&#39;&#39;xxx&#39;&#39;&#39;</code>和<code>&quot;&quot;&quot;xxx&quot;&quot;&quot;</code>_可换行显示的字符串或作为注释使用</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>输出某位(索引)</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>print(a [ len(a) - 1 ] )</code>_输出a字符串的最后一位</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#类型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"类型\"></a>类型</h2><ul>\n<li><p>字符串_str</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>整数_int</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>浮点数_float</p>\n<ul>\n<li>带有小数点的</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>布尔_bool</p>\n<ul>\n<li>True</li>\n<li>False</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>空值_NoneType</p>\n<ul>\n<li>没有任何的输入</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Type_输出对象的类型</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>type(a)</code>_输出对象a的类型</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"获取-x2F-输入\"><a href=\"#获取-x2F-输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"获取&#x2F;输入\"></a>获取&#x2F;输入</h2><ul>\n<li><p><code>input(&quot;请选择你需要的计算公式: &quot;)</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>用一个变量进行接纳</li>\n<li>input接收到的都是字符串类型,需要进行计算时需要转换为指定类型</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"总结案例-BMI值计算-判定是否健康\"><a href=\"#总结案例-BMI值计算-判定是否健康\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结案例_BMI值计算+判定是否健康\"></a>总结案例_BMI值计算+判定是否健康</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"># 计算公式: 体重&#x2F;(身高**2)\nWeight &#x3D; int(input(&quot;请输入你的体重(KG): &quot;))\nHeight &#x3D; float(input(&quot;请输入你的身高(M): &quot;))\nBMI &#x3D; Weight&#x2F;(Height ** 2)\nprint(&quot;你的BMI指数: &quot; + str(BMI))\n# 判断用户输入的数值是否异常\nif Height&lt;3:\n    # 进行BMI健康程度判定\n    if 20&lt;BMI&lt;25:\n        print(&quot;恭喜,你的BMI指数正常&quot;)\n    else:\n        print(&quot;抱歉,你的BMI指数异常&quot;)\n        if BMI&lt;20:\n            print(&#39;你太瘦啦!&#39;)\n        if BMI&gt;25:\n            print(&#39;你太胖啦!&#39;)\nelse:\n    print(&#39;请仔细查看身高的要求单位&#39;)</code></pre>","text":"2023年1月21日 字符类 &quot;xxx&quot;和&#39;xxx&#39;_字符串 &#39;&#39;&#39;xxx&#39;&#39;&#39;和&quot;&quot;&quot;xxx&quot;&quot;&quot;_可换行显示的字符串或作为注释使用 ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":945,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2023%E5%B9%B41%E6%9C%8821%E6%97%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2023年1月21日</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%B1%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">字符类</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">类型</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96-x2F-%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">获取&#x2F;输入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93%E6%A1%88%E4%BE%8B-BMI%E5%80%BC%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97-%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总结案例_BMI值计算+判定是否健康</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"梦懿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"阳光普照大地","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"测试图床上传.md","uid":"3022be9f4253ec8c4e8790e7bae873c8","slug":"测试图床上传-md","date":"2023-01-24T09:51:18.000Z","updated":"2023-01-24T12:09:15.397Z","comments":true,"pa